{"word":"ἀμφαγαπάζω","slug":"ἀμφαγαπάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀμφαγαπάζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> and <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a>\n<p/><i>to embrace warmly, treat kindly, greet warmly</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; so in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/>"}]}